rows.label: qst201801_0010
rows.name: Look at that.

rows.label: qst201801_0020
rows.name:
There's a whole lot of 'em. Maybe
we should come back later.

rows.label: qst201801_0030
rows.name:
That may be wise... Lest the
hunter become the hunted.

rows.label: qst201801_0040
rows.name: It's alright.

rows.label: qst201801_0050
rows.name:
No need to worry. Uka will
try to persuade them.

rows.label: qst201801_0060
rows.name:
Persuade... but don't you
always fail at that, Uka?

rows.label: qst201801_0070
rows.name:
Hey, maybe this time will
be a success. Right, Uka?

rows.label: qst201801_0080
rows.name: That's right. Leave it to Uka.

rows.label: qst201801_0090
rows.name: It's alright. Uka is on your side.

rows.label: qst201801_0100
rows.name: Um, where is the leader?

rows.label: qst201801_0110
rows.name: Ah, found you.

rows.label: qst201801_0115
rows.name: Um, I'd like to talk for a moment...

rows.label: qst201801_0120
rows.name: We've come to help our friends.

rows.label: qst201801_0130
rows.name:
They are Phonexes, a little
smaller and cuter than you all.

rows.label: qst201801_0140
rows.name:
They must have gathered their courage to
come here. You know of them, don't you?

rows.label: qst201801_0150
rows.name: They are not food. They are Phonexes.

rows.label: qst201801_0160
rows.name: Is Uka getting through to 'em?

rows.label: qst201801_0170
rows.name:
I wonder... The monster seems
to be in a bad mood...

rows.label: qst201801_0180
rows.name: So you're going to play dumb...

rows.label: qst201801_0190
rows.name:
I know what you've done.
Now, let the Phonexes go.

rows.label: qst201801_0200
rows.name: Oh, why won't you understand?

rows.label: qst201801_0210
rows.name: It's no use, Uka! Get out of there!

rows.label: qst201801_0220
rows.name: Ouch!

rows.label: qst201801_0230
rows.name: Are you alright, Uka?

rows.label: qst201801_0240
rows.name:
I was just trying to talk,
and you hit me. That hurt!

rows.label: qst201801_0250
rows.name:
You never listen to what people
say, you always just attack...

rows.label: qst201801_0260
rows.name: Just talk to me for a bit!

rows.label: qst201801_0270
rows.name: One for one. Now we're even.

rows.label: qst201801_0280
rows.name: I take it... the negotiations failed?

rows.label: qst201801_0290
rows.name:
Yes. Unfortunately, it seems we have
no choice but to fight, as usual...

rows.label: qst201801_0300
rows.name: Let's go!
